OL,3,CPolice issue advice after spate of
OL,4,Ckeyless car thefts
OL,6,FPolice are urging residents in to be
OL,7,Fvigilant after a spate of keyless car
OL,8,Fthefts.
OL,10,FWiltshire Police said five high-value
OL,11,Fcars have been stolen in the last week.
OL,13,FOfficers said two vehicles - a BMW
OL,14,F540i XDrive and a BMW M4 - were stolen
OL,15,Ffrom driveways in Broome Manor
OL,16,Fovernight on Thursday 7 March.
OL,18,FA third car, a Lexus RX, was also
OL,19,Fstolen from the Broome Manor area
OL,20,Fduring the same time.
