OL,6,FThe force added on Monday 11 March, a
OL,7,FMercedes Benz was stolen from Broome
OL,8,FManor, while another Mercedes was
OL,9,Fstolen from the Coate area.
OL,11,FWiltshire Police are appealing for
OL,12,Fanyone with information about the
OL,13,Fincidents to get in touch.
OL,15,FThe force has issued some security
OL,16,Fadvice for anyone who owns a keyless
OL,17,Fvehicle:
