OL,3,CPolice issue advice after spate of
OL,4,Ckeyless car thefts
OL,6,FSpare keys - When not in use, ensure
OL,7,Fall keyless fobs are protected in the
OL,8,Fsame way that the main key is
OL,9,Fprotected. If rarely used, consider
OL,10,Fremoving the battery from spare keys.
OL,12,FLocation of keys when not in use `
OL,13,FWhilst not full proof, the more
OL,14,Fcentral the keys are placed within a
OL,15,Fhome environment, the better. Do not
OL,16,Fleave keys close to the front door
OL,17,Fhowever practical/easy it may be.
