OL,3,CPolice issue advice after spate of
OL,4,Ckeyless car thefts
OL,6,FConsult your vehicle's manufacturer `
OL,7,FCustomers are encouraged to speak to
OL,8,Ftheir vehicle's manufacturer about
OL,9,Fpreventative advice including changing
OL,10,Fthe vehicle's security and convenience
OL,11,Fsettings.
OL,13,FPhysical equipment locks/aftermarket
OL,14,Fsecurity devices ` Steering wheel
OL,15,Flocks, gear lever locks or a Pedal Box
OL,16,Fare a more traditional means to deter
OL,17,Fthieves. They are also cost-effective
OL,18,Fand easily sourced.
