OL,3,CPolice issue advice after spate of
OL,4,Ckeyless car thefts
OL,6,FHome CCTV ` Do you have CCTV covering
OL,7,Fyour property and vehicle(s)? CCTV can
OL,8,Fbe a great deterrent to potential
OL,9,Fcriminals as well as offering you
OL,10,Fpeace of mind.
OL,12,FGarages ` If you have a garage, is
OL,13,Fthere space to store your keyless
OL,14,Fvehicle inside it? If so, this will
OL,15,Fnot only hide it from view, but it
OL,16,Fwill also act as a further barrier to
OL,17,Fthieves.
