OL,3,CPolice issue advice after spate of
OL,4,Ckeyless car thefts
OL,6,FDriveway gates ` Bollards and driveway
OL,7,Fgates can be effective in offering a
OL,8,Fphysical barrier to deter potential
OL,9,Fthieves.
OL,11,FNon-keyless vehicles ` These can be
OL,12,Fpositioned on the driveway either in
OL,13,Ffront of or behind a keyless vehicle
OL,14,Fso as to make it more difficult to
OL,15,Fsteal and thus reducing the chances
OL,16,Fthieves will target your keyless
OL,17,Fvehicle.
