OL,3,CPolice issue advice after spate of
OL,4,Ckeyless car thefts
OL,6,FInsurance cover ` Do you have the
OL,7,Fappropriate insurance policy to cover
OL,8,Fyour losses in the event that your car
OL,9,Fis stolen?
OL,11,FVehicle tracking devices ` Does your
OL,12,Fvehicle have a tracking device fitted?
OL,13,FIf stolen, the chances of the vehicle
OL,14,Fbeing recovered improve greatly when
OL,15,Fone is fitted.
OL,17,FValuables inside vehicles ` When a
OL,18,Fvehicle is stolen, whatever is left
OL,19,Finside it is also stolen too. Do not
OL,20,Fleave valuables on show in your car
OL,21,Fovernight unnecessarily.
